us conditions including but, not limited to:&nbsp;</span></p><ul>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Multiple missed appointments</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Patient non-adherence to the treatment plan</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Non-payment of fee owed to providers or Savant Care</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">If you fail to follow up with your provider for more than 6 months without prior authorization or have &nbsp;greater than three (3) cancellations/missed appointments within a twelve (12) month period, you will be in breach of compliance with your treatment plan and be subject to automatic discharge from Savant Care as a patient. You may return to clinic with authorization from a provider and resume receiving care at Savant Care if you wish to do so.&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">If prescriptions are lost or you have run out early more than once in a 1 year period we may decide to discharge you from the clinic if abuse or misuse is suspected.</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">If there is any evidence that you have been receiving controlled prescriptions from multiple physicians without informing your Savant Care provider, we reserve the right to discharge you from the clinic immediately.</span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"></span><br></p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our clinic policies are subject to change and you will be notified of these changes as they arise. Savant Care reserves the right to make changes to clinic policies at any time. This contract will be valid for 3 years and will be annually posted to your MyHealth Portal for review of any updated terms and conditions. &nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"p2\"><br><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><p><strong>I understand that I will