der-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">$300 for all patients</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Terms: If you fail to give notice 10 business days before your appointment, you will be charged a cancellation fee. </span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:0pt\"><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">30 minute appointment</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">15-20 minutes face-to-face, 10 minutes for documentation and other management tasks by the provider </span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;margin-right: -5.25pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">$250 for patients ages 18 and older</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;margin-right: -5.25pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">$300 for patients ages 0-17</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;margin-right: -5.25pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">$150 for all patients</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Terms: If you fail to give notice 3 business days before your appointment, you will be charged a cancellation fee. </span></p><br></td></tr><tr style=\"height:0pt\"><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Other</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">- Telephone calls with provider and email communications with provider requiring significant amounts of time will be treated as consultation with the provider and will be charged as such.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">- Coordination of care on behalf of patient requiring significant amount of time may incur an extra fee</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap