:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">- Disability documentation and other extraneous documentation will incur an extra fee. </span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;$500 per hour</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.75pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.75pt;vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">N/A</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;text-align: center;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-d29fb435-3a98-2b31-375b-bde2960a0f92\"><br></b></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-col