-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" width=\"330\" valign=\"top\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Telephone\n  calls with provider and email communications with provider requiring\n  significant amounts of time will be treated as consultation with the provider\n  and will be charged as such.</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">-\n  Coordination of care on behalf of patient requiring significant amount of\n  time may incur an extra fee</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">-\n  Disability documentation and other extraneous documentation will incur an\n  extra fee.</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"width:130.25pt;border-top:none;border-left:\n  none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\n  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" width=\"174\" valign=\"top\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  mso-add-space:auto;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">$500\n  per hour</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p></p><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:-18pt;\"><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse\"><colgroup><col width=\"110\"><col width=\"238\"><col width=\"153\"><col width=\"183\"></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height:0pt\"></tr><tr style=\"height:0pt\"></tr><tr style=\"height:0pt\"></tr><tr style=\"height:0pt\"></tr></tbody></table></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;text-align: center;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-d29fb435-3a98-2b31-375b-bde2960a0f92\"><br></b></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">OUT-OF-POCKET Track (Psychologists / Psychotherapists)</span></p></li></ul><p><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">$300/hr for psychologists and $250/hr for Master level psychotherapists.</span></span></span></font></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">*</span> <font size=\"4\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We also offer discounted rates at $200/hr for psychologists and $150/hr for Master level psychotherapists.</span></span></span></font></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Insurers may only partially cover our fees; contact your insurer for details on your out-of-network coverage. You should be aware that, in order for you to obtain reimbursement, your insurance company requires a clinical diagnosis and information about the services provided to you. Sometimes, your physician must provide additional clinical information such as treatment plans or summaries, or copies of your entire Clinical Record. In such situations, every effort will be made to release only the minimum information about you that is necessary for the purpose requested. This information will become part of the insurance company\'s records. Though all insurance companies claim to keep such information confidential, we have no control over what they do with it once it is in their hands.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">C. Cancellation Policies</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Please be mindful of our scheduling. If you arrive too late to allow time for proper care, you may be asked to reschedule. If you are more than 15 minutes late to your appointment, you will be asked to reschedule. Missed appointments prevent you from receiving required care and prevent the doctor from providing that care. It also prevents another person from receiving care during that time. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> As a result, </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">you will be financially responsible for the appointment as stated in the tables above.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">ONLY for documented emergency situations may this charge be waived or reduced at our sole discretion.</span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"> <br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Note: Insurance does NOT cover missed appointments or late cancellations. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Cancellation fees apply to both Insurance and Out of Pocket tracks. The latest fees and terms can be found at: https://www.savantcare.com/faq/t/q4-what-are-the-cancellation-charges/17</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">D. &nbsp;Payment Methods: </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;Bank ACH (direct deposit) as this proves to be the lowest cost solution for patients. &nbsp;Credit Cards and Debit Cards are accepted, but any fees charged by your credit card company will be passed on to you. As of August 1st, 2016, the fee is 4%. </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">CHECKS and CASH are accepted, but are not preferred. If check or cash is provided for payment, a $50 paper check/cash handling fee applies for each check or cash transaction. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">All charges to Credit/Debit Cards and ACH are performed within 3 business days of your appointment. All payments made will first be applied to any prior unpaid balances before current charges. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">By providing your details and signing this policy below, you are authorizing Savant Care to charge your account details provided and agree to pay all applicable charges outstanding on your patient account.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">E. OTHER: </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Savant Care may offer treatment at discounted rates if you provide proof of financial need. &nbsp;Please submit your requests to Savant Care\'s finance team. </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">NOTE: OUR INDIVIDUAL PROVIDERS DO NOT HAVE AUTHORITY TO GRANT DISCOUNTS NOR \'NEGOTIATE\' LOWER RATES WITH PATIENTS.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Savant Care and its providers DO NOT accept or participate in MEDI-CAL or MEDICAID programs. If you have this as a secondary insurance, you will be solely responsible for all charges not paid or covered by your primary insurance. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Savant Care is not liable or responsible for any disputes or issues you may have with your insurer concerning your plan\'s deductible, coinsurance, or out-of-pocket limits. It is the patient\'s responsibility to contact their insurance for inquiries or concerns related to their applicable benefits. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Note that if you are having difficulties paying your balance, or feel we may have billed you in error, please contact our office for resolution before initiating action with your financial institution. Failure to notify our office for resolution before initiating a dispute or chargeback will result in a fee of $50 for each occurrence. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:16pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For requests for paperwork that is not available electronically and not from a medical provider (i.e. Explanation of benefits, invoices above and beyond what\'s available on your MyHealth Portal, or research requests for the office staff), a surcharge of $50 will be applied for each occurrence up to 1 hour of office staff\'s time. An additional fee of $25/hour will be applied beyond the first hour per occurrence. </span><br></p>  </div>',47,'2019-01-28 13:40:13','Pacific Standard Time',2871),(99,'Collaborative care consent','<div class=\"modal-body\"><p></p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">At Savant Care, we believe that mental health can only be achieved by treating the whole person. For this reason, we have a collaborative care approach involving doctors and therapists in your treatment. To make this collaborative care model a reality, we have the following policies:</span></p><ol class=\"p1\"><li> <span class=\"s1\">Your primary provider at Savant Care is a psychiatrist. Psychiatrists are medical doctors that have extensive medical and psychological training that equip them to see the big picture of what treatments will best fit your needs. They rule out medical conditions that may be contributing to your symptoms, make outside referrals as necessary, and oversee and direct your treatment over the course of time to make sure you are improving.</span></li><li> <span class=\"s1\">Your psychiatrist may decide that you need to see a therapist and, in such a case, will make referrals to therapists within Savant Care as availability permits. Your psychiatrist will collaborate regularly with and provide supervision to your therapist about your case to make sure the treatment continues according to plan so that you meet your mental health goals.</span></li></ol><p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"></span><br></p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Patient Responsibilities:</b></span></p><ol class=\"p1\"><li> <span class=\"s1\">I understand that since my psychotherapy is being supervised by my psychiatrist, I can request my psychiatrist to be present during the therapy session or my therapist can request my psychiatrist to be present.</span></li><li> <span class=\"s1\">I understand that Savant Care will bill my insurance company for therapy appointments co-signed by my psychiatrist.</span></li><li> <span class=\"s1\">Once I have met my treatment goals, my psychiatrist may discontinue my psychotherapy.</span></li><li> <span class=\"s1\">If I do not feel the need to see a Savant Care psychiatrist, I will discuss this with my treatment team and look for a therapist outside Savant Care.</span></li><li> <span class=\"s1\">I understand that I need to meet with my psychiatrist at least once every 6 months to make sure my treatment goals are being met.</span></li></ol><p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"></span><br></p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Savant Care Responsibilities:</b></span></p><ol class=\"p1\"><li> <span class=\"s1\">Once I have completed my treatment and do not need to see a psychiatrist, I will smoothly transition to an outside therapist over a reasonable timeline that will be set by my therapist. </span></li><li> <span class=\"s1\">If my psychiatrist stops working at Savant Care for any reason, I will be matched with another psychiatrist at Savant Care. If I do not feel comfortable with the new psychiatrist, I will be matched another psychiatrist at Savant Care.</span></li><li> <span class=\"s1\">My psychiatrist and/or therapist will discuss and answer my questions about the collaborative care model upon request.</span></li></ol><p class=\"p2\"><br><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><p><strong>I acknowledge that I have read, understand, and agree to the policies and procedures as defined in this consent form.</strong></p></div>',0,'2020-03-11 16:24:23',NULL,NULL);
